Enlarge Breath			TYPE:Metabreath	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.BreathWeapon																					PRESTAT:1,CON=13																																							DESC:Your breath weapon is larger than normal. &nl; [Benefit] The length of your breath weapon increases by 50%% (round down to the nearest multiple of 5). For example, an old silver dragon breathing an enlarged cone of cold produces a 75-foot cone instead of a 50-foot cone. Cone-shaped breath weapons get wider when they get longer, but lineshaped breath weapons do not. &nl; When you use this feat, add +1 to the number of rounds you must wait before using your breath weapon again.																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.70
Improved Speed			TYPE:Monstrous																							PRERACE:1,RACETYPE=Dragon				PRESTAT:1,STR=13																																							DESC:You are faster than others of your kind. &nl; [Benefit] Your fly speed (if you have one) improves by 20 feet. All other speeds you have improve by 10 feet.																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.71
Improved Maneuverability	TYPE:General												PREFEAT:1,Hover,Wingover			PREMOVE:1,Fly=150																																																			DESC:Your maneuverability in flight improves. &nl; [Benefit] Your maneuverability improves by one category, from clumsy to poor, poor to average, or average to good (see Tactical Aerial Movement, page 20 of the Dungeon Master's Guide). &nl; [Special] You can take this feat multiple times. Each time you take the feat, your maneuverability improves by one category (but never becomes better than good).														STACK:YES	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NOCHOICE																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.70
Improved Multiattack		TYPE:Monstrous												PREFEAT:1,Multiattack																								PREWEAPONPROF:3,TYPE.Natural																													DESC:You are particularly adept at using all your natural weapons at once. &nl; [Benefit] Your secondary attacks with natural weapons have no penalty on the attack roll. You still add only 1/2 your Strength bonus, if any, to damage dealt. &nl; [Normal] Without this feat, your secondary natural attacks are made at a -5 penalty (or a -2 penalty if you have the Multiattack feat).																									BONUS:COMBAT|TOHIT-SECONDARY|2																																SOURCEPAGE:p.70
Shape Breath			TYPE:Metabreath	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.BreathWeapon																		PRESIZEGTEQ:S	PRESTAT:1,CON=13																																							DESC:You can make the area of your breath weapon a cone or a line, as you see fit. &nl; [Benefit] If you have a line-shaped breath weapon, you can opt to shape it into a cone. Likewise, if you have a coneshaped breath weapon, you can shape it into a line. When you use this feat, add +1 to the number of rounds you must wait before using your breath weapon again. &nl; [Normal] Without this feat, the shape of your breath weapon is fixed.																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.73
Suppress Weakness			TYPE:Monstrous	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.VulnerabilityEnergy	PREFEAT:1,Iron Will																													DEFINE:VulnerabilityAcidLvl|0	DEFINE:VulnerabilityColdLvl|0	DEFINE:VulnerabilityFireLvl|0	DEFINE:VulnerabilityElectricityLvl|0	DEFINE:VulnerabilitySonicLvl|0	DESC:Your vulnerability to an energy type is reduced. &nl; [Benefit] You can partially suppress your vulnerability to a type of element or energy. When subjected to an attack based on that type of energy, you take one-quarter again as much (+25%%) damage, regardless of whether a saving throw is allowed, or if the save is a success or failure. &nl; [Normal] A creature vulnerable to an element or energy type takes half again as much (+50%%) damage as normal from that energy type.														BONUS:VAR|VulnerabilityAcidLvl|1	BONUS:VAR|VulnerabilityColdLvl|1	BONUS:VAR|VulnerabilityFireLvl|1	BONUS:VAR|VulnerabilityElectricityLvl|1	BONUS:VAR|VulnerabilitySonicLvl|1	SOURCEPAGE:p.74
Overcome Weakness			TYPE:Monstrous	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.VulnerabilityEnergy	PREFEAT:2,Iron Will,Suppress Weakness																																																						DESC:You can overcome an innate vulnerability through sheer willpower. &nl; [Benefit] You can completely suppress your vulnerability to a type of energy. When subjected to an attack based on that type of energy, you take no extra damage. &nl; [Normal] A creature vulnerable to a type of energy takes half again as much (+50%%) damage as normal from that energy type, regardless of whether a saving throw is allowed, or if the save is a success or failure.																			BONUS:VAR|VulnerabilityAcidLvl|1	BONUS:VAR|VulnerabilityColdLvl|1	BONUS:VAR|VulnerabilityFireLvl|1	BONUS:VAR|VulnerabilityElectricityLvl|1	BONUS:VAR|VulnerabilitySonicLvl|1	SOURCEPAGE:p.72
